      <span class="headers">Xanthe`s Earring/PoTC - The Gifts of the Elves</span>
<p>
<p>
<i>The first three gifts come to us from elven lands. Original writeup courtesy of Xanthe Ravenwolf. Known trivials are now included, as well as links to the various sources for ingredients.</i>
</p>
<h4>First Gift of the Elves</h4>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1650&menustr=">Demi-sec Champagne</a><!-Demi-Sec Champagne->
</p>
